{"tid":2031660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：建廣西自貿區 香港融資 東盟生產 西部大開發強大需求 係咪perfect池呢 ?","createTime":"2020-05-23T14:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:58:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"fa512f066d29b8eb93fbee83f8bbadfabcd7205f","tid":2031660,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"李克強：冀廣西打造對接粵港澳大灣區合作平台<br />\n23.05.2020 21:12<br />\n<br />\n總理李克強上午出席全國人大廣西代表團會議，指廣西要發揮好沿海沿邊區位優勢，擴大對內對外開放，以建設高水平自貿試驗區、西部陸海新通道為支撐，打造對接粵港澳大灣區、面向東盟的高水平開放合作平台。李克強表示，希望廣西抓住新時代推進西部大開發形成新格局的歷史機遇，緊緊依靠各族群眾，凝心聚力抓發展保民生，努力完成全年經濟社會發展主要目標任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289681&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289681%26csid%3D261_341&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=60e39d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289681&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6ade5432e765ddcbca6418c76987832d7c1e0afb","tid":2031660,"uid":348453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0f26cb2e0b20f64e9bcce8e23fece6313fb820f","tid":2031660,"uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"搵廣西同東盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd406ae75d0b428a1e3b86316ed5b775cabf001f","tid":2031660,"uid":54721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"閪部再開發"},{"pid":"068acbbed32722922d3d8807f540bb319f6053d3","tid":